  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You focus chakra throughout your muscles enhancing your physical Dexterity and Cunning. For the duration, your Dexterity and Wisdom ability scores becomes 16 if they are lower than 16. You do not suffer fall damage from falls less than 30 feet. Your movement speed is increased by +20 feet and you gain a +2 to your passive perception.</p><p>When you would cast a Taijutsu with the Combo keyword, you gain +10 bonus to your movement speed until the end of the turn you cast it.</p>",
